To create a queue or topic within the Glassfish server’s JMS provider, go to Resources > JMS Resources > Destination Resources and click on the “New...” button.

    JNDI Name:                 jms/TestQueue
    Physical Destination Name: TestQueue
    Resource Type:             javax.jms.Queue
    Description:               Test Queue
    Status:                    [x]


    JNDI Name:                 jms/TestTopic
    Physical Destination Name: TestTopic
    Resource Type:             javax.jms.Topic
    Description:               Test Topic
    Status:                    [x]
